lyrics:
Every moment without you feels like eternity,
Lost in a world where you're all I can see.
I'm drowning in memories of what used to be,
Yearning for a love that was meant to be free.

But now I'm left here standing all alone,
Hoping for a chance to call you my own.
With every breath, I feel my heartache grow,
For without you, I'm just a shadow.
style: Chinese Electronica using erhu and suona
